name: Alma Mater
description:
I love dark cyberpunk art. I am without a doubt a melancholic. Alma Mater is a motif used in art in all of history. Even before she was called Alma Mater. Its the age all mother of the world.
This piece was, as usual, made in Procreate. I love the fact the the nft space is a place I can sell my purely digital art. So thanks to all my customers. You make this possible :)

Alma Mater
the  nourishing 
giver of life
giver of knowledge
watch over us all 
in these times of hardship
Alma Mater
unfold your arms
rise your hands and protect us all
